Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭黑團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，請先退回加爾德羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並許可我們在領地內戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為五柱之二與學園長的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹·庫魯格請求真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:00:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請許可所有僕人啓用舞鬥服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給所有加爾德羅貝學生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用舞鬥服的認證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位請一邊保護來賓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊各自撤退回學校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，妳去逮住真白公…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將彼此重疊的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖進記憶深處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟昨天不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我就站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降臨而下的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔地包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我訴說著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「守護」的真正意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾度仰望 無限寬闊的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了 那一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法再回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱切地 強烈地 勇猛地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在沒有光芒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能感覺到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你能發現我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17話\N蒼之舞／思念，飄散之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王，請振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點，真白女王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城…城堡怎樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮被擊中產生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勉強把妳們帶出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是其他人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝的技術是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能讓黑團予取予求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去砂行船的港埠？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，妳去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了，我還另有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是我女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我之所以養大妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了凪殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了阿爾泰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳，妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑團的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是幾時把城堡弄成那樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他們滲透的深度超乎預料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡還沒回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:04:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟陛下在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就還有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本學園從現在起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基於乙HiME擴散限制條約\N修正條款C
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及加爾德羅貝法典第21條
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入防衛體制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個不妙啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死就別妨礙我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照預定進行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以爭取到一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME的力量\N是我們祖先創造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳們還來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找真白女王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來的話就不會傷害你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到她的人快點招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來學園和城堡都去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真白女王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們竟然這麼“照顧”\N我的學妹們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑谷是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你們也與這場騷動有掛勾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手的不是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這並不重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接管加爾德羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決心不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現身吧，鋼之牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愕天王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該要掩護我才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼還把女王出賣給敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯，我們該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能想辦法不被抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞鬥服竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這是瞧不起我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼把舞鬥服…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主任，這到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認證系統被強力干涉波…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了，竟用這麼大的推力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統進入自閉模式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干涉波消失，學園長認可之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都被封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子，妳又…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好個黑團
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退吧，要是跟他們開打\N恐怕會破壞靈廟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，我們退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:09:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧，黎人哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣叫我，我是拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是改造人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，剩下的交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞鬥服竟然突然消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴石也可以輕易取下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝恐怕出事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是因為妳們學生\N跟五柱的主人是真祖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，這也是那些\N叫做黑團的人做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人為什麼要做這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是為了將加爾德羅貝\N隱藏的科學技術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再度廣佈到世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑團的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，我記得你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要妨礙我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會妨礙妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳們肯把真白女王交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用蒼天的青玉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有獨立主人的Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許還行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王少校，你這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放汝之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，像他那種人，幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣形勢就逆轉過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑團的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趁還沒受傷前離去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是蒼天的青玉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還沒完全使出力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是有點棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，請妳做點事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯汀小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是表現出妳信仰的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表現妳對\N偉大知識與智慧之神的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…對不…起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙…騙人的…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯，快告訴我這是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是代代身為我等\N暗中支持者的賀一族的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從出生的時候\N就受到完善的教育
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵從黑色誓約，我將實現盟約
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古代之光，知識與智慧之神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請賜我忠實的奴僕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有舞鬥服的乙HiME\N是敵不過我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸捲捲，黑團捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸捲捲，黑團捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬到舌頭了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位請冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況下才更要相信真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝200年的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會以這種形式…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來當誘餌，夏樹妳趁機…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情我哪做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如直接在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說這種天真的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳沒事，就算學園被佔領
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝就不會消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我的夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把真白交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯，妳為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是規定…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及奶奶也一直都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也對愛莉卡講過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有科學的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就可以幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再有…戰爭…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸跟奴隸領主的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和乙HiME\N與主人之間的關係一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸一旦受傷，領主也會受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳乖乖死心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就可以不用打了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，快點死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，謝爾蓋，沒想到你竟然在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是工作狂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪，你就是幕後黑手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也對\N加爾德羅貝的做法有所質疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為真的很怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠著用乙HiME這種雙刃劍\N在彼此針鋒相對之下得到和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了，妳不用擔心城市
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我的軍隊\N正從奴獸手中解放城市
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好骯髒的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是政治
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的讓真白妳自己選
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是要看朋友之間互相殘殺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是乖乖成為我的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂太深奧的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種作法不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀，真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯汀，動手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯汀，這點程度\N是打不壞乙HiME的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔…叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下，請你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩才是真正的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是溫德布倫的正當王位繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，你不是說沒找到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然認真了啊，真不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才要保護那個女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“漆黑的金剛石”\N回應妳的心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那顆傳說中的貴石為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說妮娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳能順利阻止她們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就可以原諒謝爾蓋喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有黑色貴石的吾之乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意認同我為主人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼妮娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名解放汝之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮伊娜，住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親，你太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了成為凪殿下的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有妳的存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳不在的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妳這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯，振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不…起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學什麼的…那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要…沒有戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以永遠…跟大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很…開心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是…朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.70,0:22:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.62,0:23:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易穿上舞鬥服耶\N（White Out）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這集的發展是怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是無可奈何的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可也是五柱耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我活躍一下會死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N夏樹就是要蹩腳才可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.39,0:23:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留欺負我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:23:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖啦
